Revision history for Perl module Getopt::XML.

0.52	2009-09-23 reg
        - Removed dependency on Params::Validate
        - Updated to use XML::TreePP::XMLPath >= 0.56, removing
          deprecated methods
        - Now uses Carp

0.51	2008-11-10 reg
	- Added Params::Validate dependency to Makefile to allow for
	  successful building
	- Removed reference to Pod::Usage

0.50	2008-11-03 reg
	- original version
